\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \tab \hich\f0 \ldblquote \loch\f0 Peeeeeeerfect . . .\hich\f0 \rdblquote \loch\f0  she said, prancing up to inspect them.  She turned to Paul, and with her hand to her chin she studied him, his thin frame covered by more greyish clothes, though different from what he'd been wearing the day before.  Turning back she rifled through the hills of fake hair, at last retrieving a rainbow mohawk wig.}
